{"tid":1559412,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"全新越野路華Defender登場","createTime":"2019-09-10T20:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T15:31:15.000Z","uid":236926,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1d1c35a9ba7f6774038f25ec765194338427a725","tid":1559412,"uid":236926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T20:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1MrP0pr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1MrP0pr.jpg&h=5f2cf580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n適逢車廠71週年，Land Rover正式推出全面革新的Defender車系<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9cWXosx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9cWXosx.jpg&h=ffee1c96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車型分為短陣 90，及長陣 110<br />\n<br />\n外形上保留歷史悠久的形態，但配合現今Land Rover的家族設計<br />\n<br />\n為確保新車能符合極限測試的通過標準，在合格前已進行超過 62,000 項不同的測試 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWmAbw0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJWmAbw0.jpg&h=d7ef2a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsro4R1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgsro4R1.jpg&h=c416e4bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nD7x 底盤被形容為95％新，並使用鋁合金構造，四輪獨立避震<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6dyGd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6dyGd0.jpg&h=2b9f3ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mEye97e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEye97e.jpg&h=10e6423b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與地面距離達291mm，能涉水900mm及29,38,40度角上下坡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kp5EBPC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkp5EBPC.jpg&h=4835dbc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n引擎方面有四種選擇:<br />\n197bhp 或 236bhp 的2.0柴油引擎<br />\n296bhp 直四汽油引擎 <br />\n395bhp 直六引擎配混能系統<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: large;\">全部只配備自動波箱</span><br />\n<br />\nDefender 90<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S0JCosi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS0JCosi.jpg&h=ba358cb3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8orgD0B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8orgD0B.jpg&h=87f4df79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9rX0md1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9rX0md1.jpg&h=f47aad86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aKcfUy3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKcfUy3.jpg&h=f1fa7a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 90 車型能夠以掀背車的體積，容納六位乘客<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDefender 110<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9GCC7We.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9GCC7We.jpg&h=9c809910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QLPueBf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLPueBf.jpg&h=aaad5f57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N5H0mgi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5H0mgi.jpg&h=08701aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8JuYSnZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8JuYSnZ.jpg&h=f79d84e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jo4Ruhv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJo4Ruhv.jpg&h=45aa0a30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而Defender 110 車型將提供五座，六座或 5+2 座位配置， 並在第二排座位後有 1,075 公升存物空間(放下第二排會增加至 2,380公升) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n車廂方面，比起舊Defender 可以話全面升級<br />\n中控台有部10吋 &lsquo;Pivi Pro&rsquo; touchscreen  <br />\n 地面用上橡膠物料以方便清潔<br />\n 若果車主非為越野愛好者，可選配地毯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4FXvKOF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4FXvKOF.jpg&h=5ecf7ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EqoSdG1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEqoSdG1.jpg&h=67c4593e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OizBFm1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOizBFm1.jpg&h=fc43ac25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除此之外，標準配備還有 電子調節及暖氣提供座椅, ClearSight 地面監察 鏡頭, 前後區域溫度控制, 巡航系統, 電話連接 及更多基本設備<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n越野性能方面有更多電子輔助 <br />\n Defender會是首款車型搭載 Configurable Terrain Response system，該系統會俾駕駛者在差速器，油門反應，波箱，轉向及防滑系統上調較不同的設定<br />\n若果不想麻煩，系統中有 Intelligent Auto mode，協助自動調交至當下最合適的設定 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ATsPeBr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FATsPeBr.jpg&h=428e03c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 全線車型款式會有 S, SE, HSE,  X   <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HgiuY25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHgiuY25.jpg&h=e6bb31fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外另設四款裝飾配件套裝:<br />\nExplorer<br />\nAdventure<br />\nCountry<br />\nUrban<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n110 車系定價為 &pound;45,240起(基本柴油)至&pound;78,800(基本直六汽油) <br />\n<br />\n而 90 車系會由 &pound;40,000起， 並在2020年中才會加入Defender系列<br />\n<br />\n2020年會再加入兩款商務型號，定價大約於 &pound;35,000起"},{"pid":"902449eb3664deffcc8dc3c4e8d38a9dc14330a2","tid":1559412,"uid":5172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T20:18:47.000Z","msg":"四不像<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44425f9f8abd458fd4e4cca5b3c713f5605b31c","tid":1559412,"uid":102187,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T20:19:50.000Z","msg":"嘩 好撚薯 完全冇左男人味<br />\n似toyota d 傻仔家庭車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498b20d585101905c2ca5ec6dbcec2ed45260643","tid":1559412,"uid":92836,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T20:20:47.000Z","msg":"咪一早討論過咯， 由香港人設計㗎龍獅旗<br />\n<im